    "body": "## Problem\r\nAs mentioned in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/27469, there is an inconsistency between extmarks/highlights regarding the end_col option. Now the end_col option in the nvim_buf_set_extmark function can be set to `-1 `- meaning to the end of the line.\r\n## Solution\r\nThe PR #28169 by @NStefan002 mostly does the entire fix, but somehow it was never merged.\r\nThis PR just adopts and finishes #28169.\r\nCloses #27469.",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-09T20:25:37Z",
    "comment_data": [
        {
            "_links": {
                "html": {
